title: Willingdone - Critical Period (2015) - MP3, 320 Mbps
description:
"Critical Period" was recorded in my bedroom over 
the course of several months in 2014. I was 
seventeen years old when I started making this 
EP and eighteen when it was finished. These are 
some of the first songs I've ever written and 
recorded with the intention of sharing them with 
people, and they mean a lot to me. I hope they'll 
mean something to you. Thanks for listening. 

released 06 March 2015 

Music -- Ben Rosenberg 
Cover Art -- Amy Carlson

TRACKS:

  1. Scattered
  2. The Westphall Connection
  3. Moving Caverns
  4. Sleepfell


Thanks for listening,

Ben / Willingdone
